---
title: Mediterranean Style Chopped Salad with Courgette, Croutons and Greek Style Cheese
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Mediterranean Style Chopped Salad in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
